description:
Satsuki is a serious-minded foxgirl and a bit of a workaholic. Deep down, she is quite sensitive, hoping to become a http://anidb.net/t1663 [miko] someday. Nevertheless, this only makes her work harder at Konohanatei to make up for her feelings of incompetence. She is quite fond of http://anidb.net/ch90639 [Yuzu], but not very good at showing it.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Satsuki
